sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Main
    participant G as Game
    participant B as Bird
    participant O as Obstacle
    participant S as Scoreboard
    M->>G: create game
    G->>B: create bird
    G->>O: create obstacles
    G->>S: create scoreboard
    loop Game Loop
        M->>G: start game
        G->>B: bird.update()
        G->>O: obstacle.update()
        G->>S: scoreboard.update(score)
        G-->>M: game_over
    end
    M->>G: end game
